Html:
I am not able to write big data through phpExcel my data size is around 2 MB having around 80 columns

phpExcel will not write after 1563 rows, data stuff is correct contain ascii char only no junk character is there.

That's around 125,000 cells. Rough estimate is that you need around 1 KB memory per cell with PHPExcel 1.7.0.

This means you need around 125 MB. How much memory is there available? Can you raise memory_limit ?
